args: *sigh* This heat is nigh on unbearable...
It's no wonder I went so long without\nvisiting the beach.
We sylvans are rather weak to the sun,\nafter all...
Yo Cleo, come say hi to the ocean!
I think the ocean can hear me from here.\nBesides, it's far too hot to leave the\nshade of my umbrella.
That's what the water's for, dummy!
Have your fun, Luca.\nDon't trouble yourself over me.
Eh, suit yourself.\nYo Ranzal, you ready?!
*sigh* Where do they find the energy?
The only way to beat this heat is to hide\nfrom it completely.
Or...is that merely what I want to believe?
I spent so long crafting these hair\naccessories, only to waste away the\nhours like this...
Cleo? Aren't you going to join the others?
I-I took it upon myself to watch over\nthings, in case any emergencies arise.
That, and I'm still not entirely\ncomfortable in this swimsuit...
Please, go and have fun with the others.\nI am content to chaperon.
How about we take turns, then?
It wouldn't be right if you just ended up\nwatching us the whole time.
Is that not the role of a retainer?
There's no rule that says retainers aren't\nallowed to enjoy themselves at the beach.
Perhaps not, but my duty to you takes\nprecedent over seaside frolics.
Isn't it also my duty as prince to take care\nof my people?
I appreciate your concern, Highness,\nbut I am quite capable of handling\nthis alone.
I much prefer the shelter of my umbrella,\nin any event.
Right. Well, would you mind if I sat\nbeside you then?
I'd like to keep you company.
B-but... Surely there is more fun to be had\nsplashing in the sea.
We likely won't be back here soon;\nyou should enjoy it while you can.
That's exactly why I don't want to leave\nyou sitting here alone.
If I'm intruding, though, I'll leave you be.
...You really are too kind for your\nown good, you know.
I just want you to have fun like\neveryone else.
That is precisely what I'm referring to.
I shall join the others in the water.
I won't be responsible for you missing your\nown chance at fun.
But...didn't you just say you preferred\nthe shade?
Do you want to splash around together\nor not?
You want me to enjoy myself...
And I wish you the same.
Then what are we waiting for?\nLet's get out there and make the most of it!
Try not to get TOO carried away.
...Heh. I suddenly feel I might be able\nto endure this heat.
